data.description: This amazing, one of kind home sits on an incredible 4.5 private acres! This unique house boasts an attached two car garage, PLUS another, free standing 2 car garage. Lots of space above both, to finish or use for storage.  First floor boasts a huge living/great room with wood stove, a large dining area with another wood stove, a bathroom, a laundry utility room, and even a den (or another bedroom).  On the second floor there are two large bedrooms on one side, and a beautiful private master suite on the other side of the home. A Generac on demand generator and a fenced in area for kids/dogs make this home even more amazing. This home does need a new roof and right side of the home needs some repairs.   Come see...though sold "as is" this home will not last long at this unbelievable price.  Showings to start at open house Saturday Feb. 4 from 2:00-4:00 and Sunday 12:00- 2:00.
